Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:37.97,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Are you serious！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.93,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}No No No don't worry  One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.10,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}沉默的心脏 再次传来跳动的旋律
